OL,3,CPatient being tested for Ebola at
OL,4,CGlasgow hospital
OL,6,FA hospital ward in Glasgow has been
OL,7,Fpartially closed due to a suspected
OL,8,Fcase of Ebola virus, according to STV.
OL,10,FIt is understood that tests are being
OL,11,Fcarried out on an individual who
OL,12,Farrived at the Queen Elizabeth
OL,13,FUniversity Hospital's Acute Receiving
OL,14,FUnit on Tuesday.
OL,16,FThe tests will confirm whether the
OL,17,Fpatient has contracted the deadly and
OL,18,Fcontagious disease, which has recently
OL,19,Fbe spreading rapidly in the Democratic
OL,20,FRepublic of Congo.
