OL,3,CPatient being tested for Ebola at
OL,4,CGlasgow hospital
OL,6,FUganda is also responding to an
OL,7,Foutbreak of Ebola and one case has
OL,8,Fbeen recorded in France.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FPublic Health Scotland (PHS) confirmed
OL,16,Fthat a scheme which aims to protect
OL,17,Fand monitor the health of those who
OL,18,Fmay travel from the UK to affected
OL,19,Fareas for their work has been
OL,20,Factivated.
