OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782901111
OL,3,CPatient being tested for Ebola at
OL,4,CGlasgow hospital
OL,6,FIf the individual is confirmed to have
OL,7,FEbola, it would be the first case to
OL,8,Fbe detected in Scotland since nurse
OL,9,FPauline Cafferkey underwent treatment
OL,10,Fat the country's largest hospital in
OL,11,F2016 after a recurrence of the illness.
OL,13,FShe initially contracted the disease
OL,14,Fwhile working at an Ebola Treatment
OL,15,FCentre in Kerry Town, Sierra Leone.
OL,17,FPHS added: "There are currently no
OL,18,Fconfirmed cases of Ebola in Scotland
OL,19,Fand the risk to the general public
OL,20,Fremains low."
